            . I am a constable. The prisoner was given in tomy charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182209110124"></xptr>Prisoner's Defence. I overtook a man who asked me to assist in putting the sheep aside, and let the chaise pass, and told me to tell the gentlemen to drive on. I looked down and saw the handkerchief, and picked it up.</p>
